Comment_contributor: (litː 'two hands being at the leg there one')

Comment_glosser: The form should be ‘string.bag one’ (i.e., 100[⋅]1), but ‘string.bag’ is written here exactly the same as ‘hand’, thus 5[⋅]1 = 5. Other sources show ‘hand’ and ‘string.bag’ to be phonetically similar yet distinct words

The form should be ‘string.bag two’ (i.e., 100[⋅]2), but ‘string.bag’ is written here exactly the same as ‘hand’, thus 5[⋅]2 = 10. Other sources show ‘hand’ and ‘string.bag’ to be phonetically similar yet distinct words
